messages.raw: [W:02][S:03]Hee hee! A customer! Welcome![K][2]I sell only the finest Magic[V]Beans! Plant one in soft soil,[V]and who knows what'll grow![K][3]Might be a ladder to the sky,[V]hee hee! Care to try one?[K]
[W:02][S:03]One Magic Bean for you! That'll[V]be 100 Rupees, please![K][2]Hee hee! Happy planting![K]
[W:02][S:03]Ah, you know the old melody![K][2]My beans just love a good storm.[V]It makes their magic grow extra[V]strong, hee hee![K]
